  <summary date="2019-07-26T18:07:42Z" status="Introduced in House">Chemical Assessment Improvement Act 

This bill modifies procedures related to specified chemical assessments performed by the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA). Specifically, chemical hazard identification and dose response assessments, currently performed by the Integrated Risk Information System program, must be performed by the appropriate EPA program office.</summary>
